          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The thin targets were prepared by compressing the",
                "necessary amount of the natural, high purity K-Br.",
                " The isotopic composition of the natural bromine  -",
                "Br-79-69%,",
                "Br-81-49.31%.",
                "Pellets thicknesses were obtained by the weight and",
                "area measurement.",
                "The weight of pressed K-Br pellets, diameter 1.5 cm,",
                "area 1.76 cm**2, varied throughout the stacked thin",
                "K-Br discs according to necessary energy loss of",
                "protons in each discs.",
                "About twenty K-Br pellets (0.2-0.6 g/cm2) were placed",
                "in an aluminum target holder."
              ]
            }
          ],
